2026-05-15T21:33:03.6148444Z 22    <!--
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6149011Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6149943Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6150605Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6151432Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6152238Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6153232Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6154047Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6154846Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6155635Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6156408Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T21:33:03.6156993Z 33    -->
