2026-05-15T21:33:03.9101526Z 248        <!--
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9101727Z 249            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9101931Z 250            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9102127Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9102329Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9102468Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9102689Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9102995Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9103310Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9103509Z 257            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T21:33:03.9103653Z 258            preserve via tools:node="merge".
